downloadTitle: MSDN Success Builder Module 2-002: Team Leadership
downloadDescription: Developer training materials for the Success Builder program from MSDN.
detailsSection: A guide to transforming a group of people working together into a high performance team that achieves results. This guide shows how software developers can create a team environment that encourages team members to be motivated, to develop their professional capabilities and to view themselves as responsible for the team’s results. 9 subsections. 60 minutes.
installInstructionSection: To use the course materials unzip the archive file and extract the included documents to a location on your hard drive.
